{"tid":1370850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"交通擠塞，先入屯門，轉西鐵10分鐘就到","createTime":"2019-07-27T06:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T07:48:02.000Z","uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05f3673f2e14ad9eb41bb7fd57d31e2a9543282a","tid":1370850,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"436dd943a282206f33bdaa8de71a942c1ee4e1b0","tid":1370850,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:18:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0b3904c8eee1bca7220377510f085a499553628e","tid":1370850,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7ff51d5b0857cf3e0fc1f0c3ab9bb07e3fb9117","tid":1370850,"uid":4050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不入村，不破壞，對家郁手，必定還拖</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c3830e859673e52a9bfa4676286aae4cdcc8c37b","tid":1370850,"uid":175119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9490743afa87157a4c0bc141e5087862727ba27d","tid":1370850,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:49:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07f81caf540604460372a71781114088992407e9","tid":1370850,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:50:24.000Z","msg":"雖然好多POST有講 而且都有前線手足出POST講左唔會入村<br />\n但都要再次提醒巴絲<br />\n<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不主動攻擊 不入村 受攻擊就即時還擊 執行公民拘捕令 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n去食老婆餅的巴絲帶多幾條索帶去包手信 餅盒太多條繩會頂唔順斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946a1f5cd4d870b36bbbc6cf9f754ba03ea7c05e","tid":1370850,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:50:55.000Z","msg":"可以先上天水圍車<br />\n大欖隧道轉車站落車可以轉車入元朗<br />\n<br />\n坐到天水圍轉又得，聚星樓就係天水圍站<br />\n以下路線可到達天水圍站（聚星樓巴士站）：<br />\n<br />\n69M (葵芳開出經荃灣)<br />\n69X (西九開出經佐敦至美孚)<br />\n269B (紅磡開出經尖沙咀油麻地佐敦)<br />\n269C (觀塘開出經東九龍沿途各站)<br />\n276A (上水開出直達天水圍)<br />\n969 (銅鑼灣開出途徑港島)<br />\nE34A (機場及東涌)<br />\n<br />\n天水圍站可坐西鐵直接到朗屏站、元朗站<br />\n如果西鐵已爆，天水圍站要坐輕鐵的話先上751，坑尾村轉761P入元朗大馬路"},{"pid":"6c410d66b0cc9984e65daaf1484c701c0d33cb4b","tid":1370850,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286f990a4704e148344288685071c7568093a3f7","tid":1370850,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b64441895cdc763b472809335b62375be7c4c8f","tid":1370850,"uid":183499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"用鐵路，唔好搭巴士"},{"pid":"2a81892085f4095bb0c2a6655c15e6197e871000","tid":1370850,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"美國副總統都識香港嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7df22795adbbfd60167a8fcce03635e2d6fdbe","tid":1370850,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a81892085f4095bb0c2a6655c15e6197e871000","tid":1370850,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"美國副總統都識香港嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86b1aeacff0b6b494e8304fd669477c9b8f7052","tid":1370850,"uid":291579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"條條大路通元朗"}]}